timeline.body:
Pls use AssertJ for this and future tests. If the dependency is not already added, add it like this to the corresponding
pom.xml: 	


&lt;dependency&gt;
			&lt;groupId>org.assertj&lt;/groupId&gt;
			&lt;artifactId>assertj-core&lt;/artifactId&gt;
			&lt;version>${version.assertj}&lt;/version&gt;
			&lt;scope>test&lt;/scope&gt;
&lt;/dependency&gt;


Then you can import the static assertthat...() methods

